name: Roger Misso
subject: How many political fundraising emails have you gotten today? :-)
body: Peter, It's ridiculous, isn't it? But it's necessary. Why? Because corporate PACs, Super PACs, and other dark money groups spent an average of $3,000,000 opposing each of our veteran and military family candidates of integrity for Congress last November. Regular people of good character just can't compete with that on their own. That's why we need you. Taking the Hill funds the kinds of candidates you want in public office - those who have proven their integrity over years of service to our country. And we've got a simple goal for them that isn't based on money - it's powered by people. We'll break down the math for you: -We are endorsing 22 candidates for the US House and Senate in 2022, and we want to help them each reach at least 10,000 veteran and military family voters in their districts. In total, that's more than 200,000 voters. -Whether it's door-to-door, in their mailbox, or on TV, the average cost of voter contact across all mediums last cycle was ~$5 per voter. That means that, between now and next November, we need to raise more than $1 million to win - or roughly $75,000 per month. -We're coming to you because we need to raise another $8,000 today to hit that target - and keep our good, decent, and honorable candidates on the path to victory. If every person who reads this email chips in to help us reach 10 voters today (that's just $50!) by clicking here (https://secure.actblue.com/donate/tth093021), we will exceed our goal and be able to go up on the airwaves and help get volunteers to canvas for our candidates. That's huge! As a BONUS, anyone who helps us reach more than 200 voters (by contributing $1,000 or more) will get FREE admission to the rest of our political events this year. Previous guests have included Cory Booker, Tammy Duckworth, and Raphael Warnock - you don't want to miss them! Thank you for opening this email and understanding why we write to you! We hope we're making you proud. Yours in service, Roger Roger Misso Executive Director Taking the Hill @RogerMissoCNY To make a contribution, click here: https://secure.actblue.com/donate/tth093021 Checks may be mailed to: Taking the Hill PAC PO Box 2134 Bristol, PA 19007 ----------------------------------------- | Paid for by Taking The Hill PAC | ----------------------------------------- Taking The Hill PAC PO Box 2134 Bristol PA 19007 United States If you believe you received this message in error or wish to no longer receive email from us, please https://act.myngp.com/el/ZElqZAcdItbRHoH9LYRwR9V58ApOWSPiIaqx949e2LQ=/uLMzn39VAON7Hiy269kjz2eXGeCIy37DsTOAqk5mWXs=.

body: Hi, The Democratic House majority is barely a majority – take a look:https://secure.actblue.com/donate/JHCT-05-Email-Sept2021-FR-no?refcode=E11606-20210930-EOQ2-graphic-DeadlineEOM-RegTemplate-NA-NA&amount;=25 [https://secure.actblue.com/donate/JHCT-05-Email-Sept2021-FR-no?refcode=E11606-20210930-EOQ2-graphic-DeadlineEOM-RegTemplate-NA-NA&amount;=25] While 2020 won the Democrats the White House, we did not fareso well with our House races. The GOP picked up seats and made gains – andthey are not taking their feet off the gas. With redistricting guaranteeing anRepublican pick-up of at least two seats if not more, Jahana’s frontline racehere in CT-05 is one that will make or break the Democrats’ majority in 2022and beyond. So as we approach tonight's end-of-quarter fundraising deadline,we have to show up strong – the same way we did in 2018 . We have to declarethat we will not yield this seat and we have to do so now. Tell the deeppockets not to waste their money here this year.[https://secure.actblue.com/donate/JHCT-05-Email-Sept2021-FR-no?refcode=E11606-20210930-EOQ2-SL-DeadlineEOM-RegTemplate-NA-NA&amount;=25]DONATE TO KEEP CT-05 BLUE [https://secure.actblue.com/donate/JHCT-05-Email-Sept2021-FR-no?refcode=E11606-20210930-EOQ2-SB-DeadlineEOM-RegTemplate-NA-NA&amount;=25] It’s been a busy and challenging few months – but through itall Jahana has been fighting for us. And because of our majorities, Democratswere able to get people back to work due to the American Rescue Plan, secureour right to vote, protect workers right to organize, reauthorize the ViolenceAgainst Women Act, codify the Equal Rights Amendment, end anti-LGBTQ+discrimination, support DACA recipients, and much more. Just last week, theHouse passed the Women’s Health Protection Act, which would guarantee aperson's right to reproductive autonomy. None of this would be possiblewithout our majority. Will you make a grassroots contribution right now tohelp us protect the Democratic majority and keep CT-05 blue? All of ouradvancements hinge on this crucial toss-up district! We cannot go backwards.[https://secure.actblue.com/donate/JHCT-05-Email-Sept2021-FR-no?refcode=E11606-20210930-EOQ2-SL-DeadlineEOM-RegTemplate-NA-NA&amount;=25]Thanks – we know Jahana can count on you. – Team Hayes DONATE[https://secure.actblue.com/donate/JHCT-05-Email-Sept2021-FR-no?refcode=E11606-20210930-EOQ2-SB-DeadlineEOM-RegTemplate-NA-NA&amount;=25]unsubscribe:https://email.ngpvan.com/unsubscribeUnique/b1754149-ef21-ec11-981f-501ac510a405/68c43058-4622-ec11-981f-501ac510a405?nvep=ew0KICAiVGVuYW50VXJpIjogIm5ncHZhbjovL3Zhbi9OR1AvTkdQMDMvMS82ODk4NiIsDQogICJEaXN0cmlidXRpb25VbmlxdWVJZCI6ICI2OGM0MzA1OC00NjIyLWVjMTEtOTgxZi01MDFhYzUxMGE0MDUiLA0KICAiRW1haWxBZGRyZXNzIjogImRwd2lsbGlzNjdAZ21haWwuY29tIg0KfQ%3D%3D&hmac;=ydQey34yVtv4zSG42RFDlSqWyn7ALNBiEVAJzK6IXDc=&id;=116789091Paid for by Friends of Jahana Hayes Friends of Jahana Hayes P.O. name: Hillary Clinton & Stacey Abrams
subject: Take out MTG
body: Hey Peter, its Marjorie Taylor Greene. Democrats have made me their number onetarget to defeat and remove from Congress. In fact, there are several Democratcandidates lining up to take me out. Democrats have even recruited DemocratNational Committee Super Delegate Wendy Davis to defeat me in 2022. DEFENDMARJORIE TAYLOR GREENE - CHIP IN 17.76 BEFORE END-OF-QUARTER DEADLINE She ishandpicked by the Hillary Clinton/Stacey Abrams wing of the Democrat party.They are prepared to unleash MILLIONS of dollars to take me out. Somepolitical experts even expect $15-$20 million spent against me. . . And notjust the Democrats. The Never Trump Lincoln Project and the Liz Cheney wing ofthe Republican party want me gone. This is exactly why I must ask you to chipin 17.76 right now. Tonight at midnight, I have one of the most criticalfundraising deadlines in my political career: the End-of-Quarter reports.These reports are what Democrat operatives and Fake News "journalists" combthrough just to see how strong my support is amongst the people. They usethese reports to allocate Democrat resources amongst the most vulnerableRepublicans in Congress. They even deploy Democrats from across the country toknock doors, make phone calls, write emails, and spread Fake News on socialmedia. . . All in an effort to defeat me in 2022! As you can see, I stronglyneed your help, Peter. You've stood with me before. I must ask you to standwith me again right now by chipping in 17.76 to help me DEFEAT THE DEMOCRATS.Please hurry, the deadline is midnight tonight! The bigger my campaignwarchest, the bigger chance I have to fend off Hillary Clinton's and StaceyAbrams' Democrats. I am fighting every single day to stop these socialists inCongress who want to rip this country a part and rebuild it into theirsocialist hellhole. I will never stop fighting. I will never give up. I willnever back down. hope I can count on you! -- Marjorie Taylor GreeneCongresswoman (R-GA) Paid for by Greene for Congress This message was intendedfor: dpwillis67@gmail.com You were added to the system January 17, 2021. subject: Your support could be the difference between us hitting our goal or falling short in this critical moment
body: Friend, I had to reach out one more time ahead of tonight’s deadline. My teamsays we’re still coming up a little short on our goal, but a big last-minutepush can put us over the top before we are legally required to report ourfundraising numbers. I'm a working-class personfrom North Philly, raised by two working-class parents. We moved around a lotto avoid eviction, and I watched my diabetic mom ration her insulin for mostof my childhood. So I know just how difficult and how upside-down our economyhas been for families like mine. We can change that and give working people areal voice in Washington — but it's going to require all of us to play ourpart. And I need your support. name: Adam Schiff
subject: We can’t come up short. Not now.
body: Derek, It’s not always easy being a member of Congress but it will always bethe greatest privilege. Every time I cast a vote, write a bill, or talk with aconstituent — I’m reminded of the magnitude of our work. Its importance. Itruly couldn’t be prouder to defend our country’s values and protect thefoundation of our democracy. And it never ceases to inspire me that there aremillions of Americans who share these values. Knowing that upholding ourdemocracy and creating a better future for all is essential. And that we’llall fighting for it. Even when it feels like the GOP is launching a new attackevery day, it’s impossible to even think about giving an inch when I knowthere are millions of you fighting for justice every day. In the comingmonths, I’m going to need your help. In fact, I’m counting on your supportbefore our FEC deadline in just a few hours — so we can finish the work westarted in 2020. The 2022 midterm elections are going to be an all-out battlewith the GOP, and we can’t let them win and undo all of our progress. So,Derek, I’m humbly asking — can you pitch in right now to help my defense ofour House majority? With the FEC deadline hours away, I’m counting on those ofyou who can afford to chip in to have my back — because you can always counton me to have yours. subject: Two More For Freedom
body: We are proud to announce two more endorsements of principled, fighting,American First conservatives running to take back the HoView this message in your browser ![House Freedom Fund](http://e.conservativefwd.com/rd/9z2zldh4omh25m4fnoj39v24vgj1quse941ti7e1l28_rp22sh2s8i66pj6c1h6cp72c9h2bs)  ![Anna Paulina Luna \(FL-13\)](https://d15k2d11r6t6rl.cloudfront.net/public/users/Integrators/BeeProAgency/353616_332651/anna-paulina-luna.jpeg)  _Anna Paulina Luna, Candidate for Congress, FL-13_ Fellow Patriot:  We are proud to announce two more endorsements of principled, fighting, American First conservatives running to take back the House of Representatives next year.  First, HFF endorses **Anna Paulina Luna** for Congress in Florida’s 13th District. This will be an open seat in the 2022 elections, so the path is wide open for a great conservative candidate to win.  And GREAT is the only word to describe Anna.  She is a warrior, literally. She grew up in some of the roughest neighborhoods in Los Angeles – and fought her way out by enlisting in the Air Force after high school. She learned conservative values the hard way – by watching what government dependency, illegal immigration, and lawlessness did to her community.  Anna embodies the American Dream, which is why she has been endorsed by President Donald Trump. | |  ---  **_"Anna is a warrior, she is a winner, and it's time for all America FirstRepublicans to unite behind her strong campaign." – President Donald J.Trump_**| ---  **Please support Anna Paulina Luna today!**You may already know Anna from her work with Turning Point USA as a tirelessadvocate for conservative principles and policy. She and her husband, Andy, afellow veteran who won a Purple Heart in Afghanistan, work with non-profitsserving the veteran community. As you may remember, Anna came up just short in this district in 2020 upagainst a corporate-backed incumbent. He doesn’t want a rematch, so next yearFlorida’s 13th District will be an open seat – and conservatives around thecountry are rallying to Anna’s side.**Please help send Anna Paulina Luna to Congress now!**| ---  ![Eric Burlison\(MO-07\)](https://d15k2d11r6t6rl.cloudfront.net/public/users/Integrators/BeeProAgency/353616_332651/Eric-Burlison.jpeg)_Eric Burlison, Candidate for Congress, MO-07_We are also proud to endorse **Eric Burlison** for Congress in Missouri’s 7thDistrict.Eric is a Missouri state Senator with the #1 most conservative voting recordin the state legislature. He has fought woke socialists in his state, and nowhe’s ready to take the fight to Congress.Eric is not just a true America First conservative. He’s also a proven leader.The Left has hit him with everything they’ve got for years – and he’s stillfighting back, on the issues that matter most: election integrity, the rightto life, border security, and our constitutional rights.He won’t crack under pressure. Instead, he will apply much-needed pressureagainst Nancy Pelosi, Joe Biden, and Kamala Harris.**Please support Eric Burlison for Congress today!**Eric and Anna now join our other priority House candidates: ✅ U.S. Rep. Yvette Harrell (NM-02) ✅ U.S. Rep. Lauren Boebert (CO-03) ✅ U.S. Rep. Scott Perry (PA-10)With your help, they will all join Jim Jordan, Byron Donalds, Marjorie TaylorGreene, Andy Biggs, and the rest of the House Freedom Caucus in the fight forAmerica's future next year.**Please join us in supporting them now. Help Anna, Eric, and the rest of ourpriority candidates today!**Thank you for being part of our team and for doing so much to help us promoteprincipled leadership in Washington.Sincerely,![RayYonkura](https://d15k2d11r6t6rl.cloudfront.net/public/users/Integrators/BeeProAgency/353616_332651/Ray%20Yonkura%20Sig.png)Ray YonkuraExecutive DirectorHouse Freedom Fund| ---  **END OF THE MONTH****COUNTDOWN**![motionmailapp.com](https://s.mmgo.io/t/BsT7)| ---  **DONATE**| ---  _**"The House Freedom Fund helps grassroots candidates get the financialsupport they need to compete with establishment candidates." – Congressman JimJordan (R-OH)**_![Jim Jordan\(R-OH\)](https://d15k2d11r6t6rl.cloudfront.net/public/users/Integrators/BeeProAgency/353616_332651/Jim-Jordan.jpg)| ---  ![Image](https://d15k2d11r6t6rl.cloudfront.net/public/users/Integrators/BeeProAgency/353616_332651/HFF-Logo-Small.png)House Freedom Fund 300 Independence Ave SE Washington, DC 20003House Freedom Fund (HFF) is a multi-candidate political action committee thathelps elect conservative candidates to the U.S. House of Representatives. name: John Castorani
subject: Do you have 30 seconds to read over this?
body: Castorani for Virginia I spent six years cleaning the mess Hillary Clintoncreated when she refused to take a 4 a.m. phone back in 2012 Today I'm askingyou to help me give back to the men and women of the national guard who arestepping up to protect our communities in this time of uncertainty. Don't wantto receive our emails? Unsubscribe here. Peter, My name is John Castorani,and like a lot of other political candidates whose emails wind up in yourinboxI’m hoping you’ll give me 30-seconds to a minute to explain why I’mreaching out to you today. I’m a 29-year-old conservative from centralVirginia and I love this country of ours with all of my heart. Until earlierthis year I was a member of the United States intelligence community. Ideployed seven times with the Army’s Special Operations Command huntingradical Islamic terrorists across the Islamic MAGREB and in continentalAfrica. The men my team and I were charged with hunting down and capturing, inevery case, posed an existential threat to democratic countries around theworld, andI’m proud to say for that for 11 years my job was to track down andeliminate threats to your family and my own. Upon the election of Joe Bidento the presidency I gave up my career in the intelligence service – along withmy security clearance – to run for Congress . I did this because I’m scaredto death that Biden is going to repeat the same mistakes of President Obama,and we’re all going to pay the price. If your interest is still piqued, I’mcounting on you to continue reading. As I said, I’ve given up my career to runfor Congress with the intention of holding Washington bureaucrats moreaccountable, and in a moment, I’m going to humbly ask for your financialassistance regarding my campaign. You may recall the attacks on the UnitedStates consulate in Benghazi, Libya, on the 11th of September 2012 (the 11thanniversary of the September 11th attacks). These attacks were carried out byan al-Qaeda affiliate called Ansar al-Sharia and resulted in the deaths of theAmerican ambassador to Libya, Christopher Stevens,who became the firstAmerican ambassador to die in the line of duty in more than three decades –along with three additional American security/foreign service personnel. Thispolitical assassination made my blood boil. During my six years huntingterrorists in Africa, targeted political killings like the ones that tookplace in Benghazi reminded me – even in the worst of times – that our freedomisn't free at all.We have to fight for it. HELP ME FIGHT FOR YOU MAKE A GIFTTODAY ›› Depending on who you ask, the Benghazi attack was either a randomattack or a pre-meditated campaign of murder. But the fact of the matter isthis: An American ambassador was killed in the line of duty and politicianspointed fingers at each other over who was responsible. That BS is thereasonI’m running for Congress, and today I’m asking if you’ll chip-in $5 or$10 to help me get my campaign off the ground. At the time of the Benghaziattacks, Hillary Clinton knew that she would be running for President in 2016.Sheknew that these attacks weren’t random as she suggested, and that as thesecretary of State she would be held accountable. So, like a good career out-of-touch politician, Mrs. Clinton engaged in a campaign of smoke andmirrors,purposefully leading the American public to believe this was a randomattack, when in fact she told her daughter, Chelsea, the very same eveningthat the attacks took place that they were pre-meditated by an al-Qaeda ally.Hillary Clinton’s deceptions and lies will forever stand to serve as primeexamples of everything that is wrong in Washington. I’m running to hold thesebureaucrats accountable and I hope you’ll help put some wind in my sails bydonating $5, $10 or even $50 today . HELP ME FIGHT FOR YOU MAKE A GIFT TODAY›› In service John Castorani Republican Candidate for Congress VA-07 P.S. Ihave no money to invest in this campaign. What I do have is a lot of pride,which makes it hard to ask for financial assistance, so please, if you can,chip in $5 or $10 today to help send me to Congress and hold careerpoliticians accountable. Paid for by John Castorani for Virginia

subject: Let's accomplish this mission
body: Erik Aadland for Senate In the army, I learned the importance of helping myteammates. Will you help me Peter? The first thing I learned in the army isthe importance of teamwork. Peter, I’m honored to have you on my team, butright now,I need your help. END OF QUARTER >>> CHIP IN NOW Our mandatorythird-quarter fundraising deadline is tonight, and we are still $13,560 behindour fundraising goal. If we don’t reach our goal, we will not have theresources we need in order to stop Chuck Schumer and Nancy Pelosi. Peter, Iknow you have already done so much, but I need your help so we can win backthe Senate.Will you chip in $100, $50, $25, or anything you can to help mestop Chuck Schumer and his liberal allies? END OF QUARTER >>> CHIP IN NOW Weare living in a divided country Peter, we need to unite to secure the Americandream for our children and grandchildren.Please, before it’s too late, chip innow and help me stop the radical left. Help me make history by chipping inbefore midnight tonight Peter, help me be the reason we flip Colorado and theSenate back to the GOP. END OF QUARTER >>> CHIP IN NOW Sincerely, ErikAadland END OF QUARTER >>> CHIP IN NOW Erik Aadland is a father, a West Pointgraduate, a former Army officer, and steadfast conservative. He servedvaliantly in combat operations in Iraq and Afghanistan, and now he's runningto represent Colorado in the United States Senate. If you believe Americadeserves less politicians and more public servants,please support Erik Aadlandfor U.S. Senate. name: Herschel Walker
subject: Can you spare 16 seconds today?
body: Herschel Walker for Senate I recorded a video message on my phone for you. Canyou spare 16 seconds to watch it today? I recorded a video message on my phonefor you. Can you spare 16 seconds to watch it today? Fellow Conservative –This is a very important week for our campaign. If you've looked at yourcalendar recently, you know the end of the 3rd quarter is TONIGHT AT MIDNIGHT.For most folks, September 30th doesn't mean much. For us, it is a criticaldate BECAUSE after midnight TONIGHT, we'll have to make public what we havebeen able to raise for our Senate campaign since announcing just four weeksago. Fellow Conservative, would you please spare 16 seconds of your time andwatch the video I recorded for you? Then, if you're able to make a gift toour campaign, please consider doing so. Come next week, the entire countrywill know the strength of our campaign – and I want everyone to know we arestrong enough to win. I need your support to hit all of our goals while thereis still time left. Here are three reasons why our Q3 numbers are important:* My opponent already has $10 million in his war chest, and National Democratsjust announced they are spending millions of dollars to launch the earliestground game ever seen in Georgia. We need immediate resources to fight back. *Political pundits will look at our numbers to gauge the strength and depth ofour fundraising operation. * The amount raised in the 3rd quarter will send asignal to potential donors about our prospects of winning this race. I hopeyou're in my corner, Fellow Conservative. Thank you, Herschel Walker WatchNow → PAID FOR BY TEAM HERSCHEL, INC.

name: Jose Castillo
subject: Hispanics are walking away from the do-nothing Democrats
body: Jose Castillo for Congress The Democrat’s socialist agenda does not align withHispanic’s conservative values any longer. News alert: Hispanics are no longerall Democrats. We left behind socialist countries and we won’t let Americabecome a socialist nation. Fellow American – – Democrats think that to beHispanic, you must vote Blue. We should welcome them to the 21st centurybecause, I don’t know if you’ve heard –but Hispanics are no longer allDemocrats. That’s right, thanks to former President Donald Trump’s common-sense policies and the liberal’s insane socialist logic, the tides areturning.The Democrat’s socialist agenda does not align with Hispanic’sconservative values any longer. Frankly, it’s racist that Democrats think thatskin color has anything to do with political ideology. You may not know me, soI want to take a minute to introduce myself. My name is Jose Castillo. I wasborn in New Orleans but grew up in Honduras with a strong, single motherbefore returning to the United States. I now live in Florida with my beautifulwife and daughter, living the American dream. This is me during DonaldTrump’s ‘Save America’ Rally in Florida in July After witnessing the Democratsdestroy Donald Trump’s America-First agenda, I decided to run for Congress inFlorida’s 9th district. I’m a pro-life, pro-2nd Amendment, and pro-AmericaFirst conservative. I know what it's like to live in a corrupt country.There's a reason I left it behind – and I don't want those socialist policiesto be implemented into America.It would be an honor if you would chip in $10to help elect a Hispanic conservative from Florida to take on the Democratsand make Congress great again. Make Congress Great Again Support Jose »Hispanics are walking away from the racist, do-nothing Democrats once and forall. Their ‘values’ do not equate to the same things we want. We want secureborders, an open economy, common-sense policies, and we strongly opposeallowing the U.S. to become a socialist nation. We want liberal logic out ofour lives. Here’s the deal – Republicans only need to pick up FIVE seats nextyear to win back the House, and I can tell you we have a real opportunity tounseat a Democrat and flip a blue seatRED! If you could chip in just $5 rightnow, you’ll send me to Washington to be a voice for all conservatives againstthe RINOs and socialist Liberals. Make Congress Great Again Support Jose »Thank you for your time, I look forward to fighting for our sharedconservative values and making Congress GREAT (Republican) again! God Bless,Jose Castillo Republican for Congress Make Congress Great Again Support Jose »PAID FOR BY JOSE CASTILLO FOR CONGRESS Jose Castillo for Congress PO Box 2651Davenport, FL 33836 Don't want to receive any more of our emails? We hate tosee you go, but you can unsubscribe here .

name: Rand Paul
subject: It ends tonight!
body: [Rand Paul For Senate](https://secure.randpaul.com/donate) Dear Patriot, Theday has arrived. This will be the last you hear from me about the urgentdeadline we are up against. And it comes at a critical time -- because I justsent the Left into a manic fury. Yesterday I stood on the Senate floor andexposed Planned Parenthood for stealing taxpayer money. Now they're gettingtheir revenge on me by pouring money into my Senate opponent's campaigncoffers. For the past week, I've been warning you about this. I've struck blowafter blow against the Left, but like a wounded animal, they're striking backwith vicious rage. That's how important tonight's deadline is. Our ability tofight back against the Left hinges on it -- and YOU are the key player. Soplease don't wait another minute. I need your help -- badly. [Can I count onyour immediate contribution of $100, $50, $25, or$10?](https://secure.randpaul.com/donate) You see, unlike establishmentpoliticians, I don't have lobbyists and special interests shoveling money intomy campaign. All I have is Americans like you. I'm so proud of the work I'vedone fighting for your freedom against the D.C. insiders. But that work canonly continue if I have enough resources. [That's why it's so important thatyou join with me tonight. Can I count on your immediate contribution of $100,$50, $25, or $10?](https://secure.randpaul.com/donate) The clock is tickingand there are only a few hours left. America is at a crossroads, and my entirepurpose in Washington is to reinvigorate this great country with our foundingprinciples of individual liberty. *** I have fought back against the enemiesof freedom, like Anthony Fauci, at every turn. *** I have taken on Joe Biden'sunconstitutional power grabs, even when the media has attacked me for it. ***I have called out the abortion profiteers at Planned Parenthood, even asthey've poured money into my opponent's campaign. That's why they’re sodesperate for revenge -- because I exposed them. And that's also why I need tohave the resources to continue this fight and not allow them to win. [This isa battle for the soul of America. Will you please contribute $100, $50, $25,or $10 immediately so I can continuefighting?](https://secure.randpaul.com/donate) Tonight, all eyes are on me.And I need you to have my back. In Liberty, Rand Paul [Rand Paul, MD][Donate](https://secure.randpaul.com/donate) P.S. The deadline is TONIGHT. Andthe Left has never been more furious at me. Just yesterday I stood on theSenate floor and exposed Planned Parenthood for stealing taxpayer money. Nowthey're getting revenge on me by pouring money into the campaign coffers of myDemocrat opponent. Tonight will be a turning point in my upcoming Senate race.If my performance tonight is strong, it will put the radical Left on theropes, and give me the resources I need to stop them. [I need you tonight,more than ever. Will you stand with me by contributing $100, $50, $25, or $10immediately?](https://secure.randpaul.com/donate)[Donate](https://secure.randpaul.com/donate) Paid for by Rand Paul for USSenate No longer want to receive these emails?[Unsubscribe](https://manage.kmail-lists.com/subscriptions/unsubscribe?a=JzRcUK&c;=LBCHN2&k;=806725c802db31060a85767802131f0d&m;=Un4Gqt&r;=HWe7KcK).RANDPAC PO Box 72598 Newport, Kentucky 41072

subject: We’re watching the clock tonight ⏰
body: [https://act.johnfetterman.com/go/388?refcode=em20210930-2841-header&t;=1001&akid;=2841%2E434096%2EYe9Rx-]John Fetterman Hi Peter — it’s John here. This evening, you’re hearing from alot of the campaigns that you support. And there’s a good reason for that.Tonight at midnight, our campaign is required by federal law to publiclyreport exactly how much we’ve raised this quarter to the FEC. [https://act.johnfetterman.com/go/32326?refcode=em20210930-2841&t;=1002&akid;=2841%2E434096%2EYe9Rx-]That makes tonight’s deadline at midnight one of the most important nights ofour campaign. And in these final hours, I’m here to ask for your support withonly one emotion in my and Gisele’s hearts: Gratitude. This campaign hasalways been about the issues that are impacting families across ourCommonwealth. It’s about transparency and faith — but it’s also deeply rootedin belief. And I’m grateful that you’re here with our team, because it meansyou believe in what we’re working towards, too. [https://act.johnfetterman.com/go/32326?refcode=em20210930-2841&t;=1003&akid;=2841%2E434096%2EYe9Rx-][IMG] I’m grateful to the people across Pennsylvania who have opened theirdoors and ears to hear about the values that I’m running on to be your 51stDemocratic vote in the U.S. Senate. name: Roger Roth
subject: Inflation Survey – Response Requested!
body: How is inflation hurting your family's bottom line? Friend, I have written ALOT about budgets lately... You expect your government to live within itsmeans, and that's exactly what Republicans did with our conservative balancedbudget. But family budgets are just as important. Prices are rising oneverything from gas to groceries, and it's threatening to undo the progresswe've made here in Wisconsin. TELL MADISON >> IS INFLATION HURTING YOURFAMILY? Gas, groceries, housing, back-to-school shopping... EVERYTHING costsmore this year. Inflation is a government-created problem, caused by big-spending bureaucrats who would rather keep you home than let America work. InWisconsin, that means families are facing tough choices as the bills growbigger and the paychecks don't. Help me make Madison understand by signing myrunaway inflation petition. name: Pramila Jayapal
subject: I won’t let them block Medicare expansion, child care, paid leave and climate action
body: [1]Pramila Jayapal Peter, People across this country want economic relief andurgent action to address climate change, and they want corporations to finallypay for it. That’s why I’m leading the charge to guarantee Democrats pass thePresident’s Build Back Better Act. For far too long, conservatives have letcorporate America write the laws that allow fossil fuel companies to destroyour environment, Big Pharma to profit while people ration insulin, and WallStreet to hit it big while hunger and homelessness increase in America. That’swhy progressives are flexing our muscle on Capitol Hill — the people demand itand deserve it. We are withholding our votes on a small bill until Democratspass President Biden’s Build Back Better Act to expand Medicare, secureuniversal child care, pre-K, and community college, fight climate change, andinvest in affordable housing. We’ve had to cancel all of our in-person fundraisers for the rest of themonth. name: Carolina Serrano
subject: What AOC got wrong
body: Carolina Serrano for Congress When I’m not fending off the radical Democrats,I spend my time working, earning a living as a waitress. Fellow Conservative– in 2016, no one in Washington had uttered the name AOC ever before. In 2016,AOC was bartending and waitressing to put food on the table. To pay rent. Sameas me. But here’s the major difference: I know what it’s like to make endsmeet – to not know if your paycheck will be enough to ensure you eat afterpaying bills, to scrounge and fight hard to give yourself a better life. But Iget by without the socialist policies. Without relying on the governmenthandouts and expecting them to foot the bill of me. I’m accountable for myselfand you’ll never hear me whine about pushing up my sleeves and getting the jobdone. My name is Carolina Serrano, I’m a Colombian-American woman andRepublican candidate for Congress. When I’m not fending off the radicalDemocrats, I spend my time working, earning a living as a waitress. I’mrunning for Congress because we are suffering at the hands of the do-nothingDemocrats. Hardworking Americans are struggling with soaring inflation andout-of-control government spending. I’m not your typical politician, I justlove America and what to ensure we are getting the best this country has tooffer. Will you make a donation to my campaign today to help elect a hard-working, every-day Conservative to Congress? $10 ➔ $25 ➔ $50 ➔ Give More ➔Here’s the thing, Fellow Conservative . I think that Congress is overrun bycareer politicians and people with the wrong motives. We need regular peoplein Congress – that know what it’s like to earn a living and make sacrifices.People like me and you. I want to build the wall, protect our freedom, and putan end to the wasteful spending that’s robbing hard-working Americans.But Ican’t do it without your help. Democrats don’t know my name today. But I’mtheir next biggest nightmare – that will deliver real change to this countryand protect the interest of hard-working Americans. Can I count on you to helpme make it happen today? Por la Libertad, Carolina Serrano RepublicanCandidate for Congress Follow Carolina On Social Media PAID FOR BY CAROLINAFOR CONGRESS Don't want to receive any more of our emails? We hate to see yougo, but you can unsubscribe here .

name: Cheri Beasley
subject: What I’ve learned from winning statewide before
body: Hi friend - I’m personally reaching out today to share a bit about the kind ofcampaign we need to run to win North Carolina and why tonight’s FEC deadlinematters so much to our success. The typical kind of Senate campaign we’ve seenin North Carolina hasn’t worked for Democrats frankly. That’s why I’ve saidfrom day one that we have to try something different. What I’ve learned frommy previous statewide campaigns is that we really need leaders who focus onthe people they serve. We must speak to the hopes and needs of every NorthCarolinian — particularly those who have been left behind and ignored byWashington for so long. And in a tough race like this, we will need to buildthe largest grassroots movement our state has ever seen to mobilize voterseverywhere. Reporting a strong number after tonight’s deadline will send apowerful message that we have what it takes to do just that. So can you make a$3 donation to our campaign before our FEC deadline at midnight? I cannot winthis race for U.S. Senate alone. It will require all of us to come together aspart of this bottom-up, grassroots effort.[https://secure.actblue.com/donate/cb-em-sep21/?refcode2=a8405204-1322-ec11-981f-501ac510a405] Look, Republicans knowour campaign is one of Democrats’ prime opportunities to flip a seat andexpand the Senate majority. That’s why they’re already funneling so much moneyinto this race. But I have faith that, with your help, we’ll be ready forwhatever they throw our way. They are no match for what we can achievetogether. name: Adam Schiff
subject: Government shutdown
body: Derek, Right now, the news coming out of Washington is confusing. But let’snot overcomplicate this: Republicans passed a $2.3 trillion tax cut forbillionaires and corporations in 2017. And they racked up almost $7 trillionin other debt. And now they’re refusing to pay for it. Worse? They’re usingthat talk of debt to try to tank Democrats’ efforts to put forward programs onhealth care, child care, climate action, and much more. It’s really thatsimple. That’s Republican brinkmanship. Threatening a dangerous outcome ifthey don’t get what they want. And it could prove disastrous if they followthrough with a government shutdown. They’re threatening to default on theUnited States’ federal debt right as we negotiate to pass a once-in-a-generation investment in American infrastructure and families. That would meanmillions of jobs lost. Families pushed into poverty. Not to mention settingoff a global financial crisis. For Americans working to make ends meet — itwould be a catastrophe. name: Nancy Pelosi
subject: a DEVASTATING blow
body: I know I don’t normally send you emails this long, but it’s so important to methat you know what’s happening behind the scenes in our fight for the House.If you have a minute, it would mean everything to me if you read my entiremessage. Then, can I count on your $5 to defend my House Democrats? >>https://links.e.dccc.org/els/v2/z7- NEWS: DEMOCRATS’ HOUSE MAJORITY IS IN JEOPARDY I’m in complete disbelief.NBC just announced my House Majority is in severe danger. Republicans onlyneed to flip FIVE seats to regain the Majority. And I just watched them launcha massive wave of attack ads against ELEVEN of my most vulnerable Democrats. Irefuse to let Republicans attack my Democrats and unseat our criticalMajority. I can fix this, but not if we fail to meet my critical End ofQuarter goal before my deadline in just 15 hours. Can I count on your helpright now to protect our House Majority? >>https://links.e.dccc.org/els/v2/Eqxzt_ NEWS: REPUBLICANS SHATTER FUNDRAISING RECORDS TO RETAKE THE HOUSE I can’toverstate the severity of this situation. Republicans have posted record-breaking fundraising SIX months in a row. Kevin McCarthy has already raised$43 MILLION this year. Trump’s shady political groups have $102 MILLION in thebank. And we’re on the brink of falling short of my MASSIVE End of Quartergoal. I need you to make a crucial choice at this moment. We can letRepublicans take our House Majority and barge back into power -- or we canrise up, send a historic response, and stop them from EVER holding poweragain. But if we fail to meet my crucial End of Quarter goal before time runsout on my deadline in just 15 hours, it will be a devastating blow to ourchances of keeping the House. I’m counting on you right now more than you knowto protect our House Democrats >>https://links.e.dccc.: DEMOCRATS AND REPUBLICANS NECK AND NECK IN POLLS I need you tounderstand. Our House Majority is RAZOR-thin. Republicans only need to flipFIVE seats to take it from us. And our polling lead is gone. Every fundraisingrecord Republicans shatter brings them closer and closer to winning the HouseMajority once and for all. I know I ask a lot of you, but this is quitepossibly my most urgent ask. Meeting my End of Quarter goal before my deadlinein 15 hours could define Democrats’ chances of HOLDING the House Majority andensuring Republicans NEVER hold power again. I need you to remember how hardwe worked to gain this Majority, and how many lives have improved because ofit. I know we will never forgive ourselves if we let Republicans take it fromus. name: Tyler Smith
subject: No, the sky is not falling, but...
body: # [#]Listen, At this point, I’m sure you’re getting inundated with emails frompeople saying the sky is falling and that you have to give to their campaignright now. Obviously, the sky is not falling. But, I’m reaching out to makesure you know the importance of this end-of-quarter deadline. With this racegrowing in both significance and the amount of people running, we can’t slowdown. Slowing down signals to everybody — our opponents, dark-money groups,and grassroots supporters — that we may not have what it takes to defeat RonJohnson in just over a year. A donation of just $5 will help us hit our end-of-quarter goal by tomorrow at midnight. We still need to raise $9,825 bythen. Chip in now >> [https://secure.actblue.com/donate/nelson-sep21-eoq?amount=5]If you've stored your payment information with ActBlueExpress, your donation will be processed immediately. DONATE $5 NOW »[https://secure.actblue.com/donate/nelson-sep21-eoq?amount=5&express;_lane=true] DONATE $25 NOW »[https://secure.actblue.com/donate/nelson-sep21-eoq?amount=25&express;_lane=true] DONATE $50 NOW »[https://secure.actblue.com/donate/nelson-sep21-eoq?amount=50&express;_lane=true] DONATE $100 NOW »[https://secure.actblue.com/donate/nelson-sep21-eoq?amount=100&express;_lane=true] DONATE $250 NOW »[https://secure.actblue.com/donate/nelson-sep21-eoq?amount=250&express;_lane=true] ANOTHER AMOUNT »[https://secure.actblue.com/donate/nelson-sep21-eoq?amount=10] I’ve said thisbefore, and I’ll say it again: Tom is exactly what Wisconsin, and our wholecountry, deserves in a Senator. I wouldn’t be working for him if I didn’tbelieve that. name: MaggieHassan.com
subject: What this FEC deadline means
body: Team – You're probably getting a lot of emails about an "upcoming FECfundraising deadline." Well, let us explain what that deadline means and whyit's so important. The Federal Election Committee (FEC) collects and reportsevery federal campaign's activity, including what they've raised and spentevery fiscal quarter. These reports are then published, giving politicalpundits and opponents a look into the strength of a campaign. Tomorrow is thenext FEC deadline, and right now, our numbers are not where they need to be.With McConnell's hand-picked candidate eyeing this seat and another far-rightcandidate already in the race, we cannot afford to fall short.
